<div id="content">        <div class="spacer"></div>             <span id="shash-73138"><div class="post" id="post-73138">                    <h1><a href="http://trilema.com/2017/time-to-get-out-by-the-way/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Time to get out, by the way.">Time to get out, by the way.</a></h1>                        <div class="date">                                     Saturday, 20 May, Year 9 d.Tr.&nbsp;|&nbsp;Author: <a href="http://trilema.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by Mircea Popescu">Mircea Popescu</a>                                                        </div>

                        <div class="entry">
<p>Let's quote from as fine a representative of the retards as could ever be had : the <a href=http://blogs.ams.org/inclusionexclusion/2017/05/11/get-out-the-way/>american mathematical society</a>. They say : </p>
<blockquote><p>Not to alarm you, but I probably want you to quit your job, or at least take a demotion. Statistically speaking, you are probably taking up room that should go to someone else. If you are a white cis man (meaning you identify as male and you were assigned male at birth) you almost certainly should resign from your position of power. That’s right, please quit. Too difficult? Well, as a first step, at least get off your hiring committee, your curriculum committee, and make sure you’re replaced by a woman of color or trans person. Don’t have any in your department?  HOW SHOCKING.</p></blockquote>
<p>It so happens that we find ourselves at a very strange point in history : for once, the view of the retards and smart people, of the inferior and of the superior, of the subhuman and the properly human actually converge! </p>
<p>After a few decades of hallucinated "revolution" against imagined "opression", the stupid women, the stupid coloreds and the stupid faggots finally come to affirm openly that which they supposedly started out by denying (only to then pivot into "combatting") : the simple and you'd think self-evident truth that stupid women, stupid ethnics and stupid faggots are actually inferior to average straight white men. </p>
<p>It was a long journey from Irigaray's <a href="http://trilema.com/2010/feminismul-inteles-drept-cult/#selection-27.0-27.120">inept nonsense</a>, but they finally made it! Considering the diminutive intellectual powers arrayed on that team, the accomplishment should, perhaps, be even more highly regarded. Do you think a really fat kid who manages to not eat more than five pies in one sitting is worthier of praise than a normal kid who manages the same ? So then! Let's take a brief moment to congratulate the stupid women, the stupid coloreds and the stupid faggots for their incredible accomplishment in taking less than half a century to realise the obvious ; after which brief moment let's move on with our lives -- the only lives that do matter, and the only lives which could concievably matter.</p>
<p>It's time to get out. The empire of idiots has no future. There's no meat left on the bones, there's no blood left to course through the veins. If indeed you are on some sort of hiring committee, or curriculum committee, or whatever other committe : yes, it's time to quit. You have no business further sullying your good name nor any real reason to continue wasting your effort. Water and oil do not mix, and there is nothing for a thinking man to do in the company of idiots and imbeciles. Leave, quit, exit now ; and by all means -- do make sure your replacement will be some stupid woman/colored/faggot. They totally earned it, and certainly deserve it. Rats belong on the sinking ship. Conscious of this natural imperative, they helpfully aim to jump to the sinking ship. Why get in their way ? Let them do the right thing, and do the right thing in letting them.</p>
<p><span style="background-color:#d3d3d3" id="select">Once rid of the time-, resources- and energy sinks, The Most Serene Republic -- the world's only <em>possible</em> sovereign -- awaits you. There is no equality, here. There is no "human dignity", certainly not of the "stupid women, stupid coloreds and stupid faggots should get the same thing you're getting" variety. There's no right to life, nor any consideration, however cursory, given to the perpetuation of life, intellectual or biological, for the stupid (not that anything keeps you from chaining up whatever fuckholes you prefer). There's no <a href="http://trilema.com/forum-logs-for-30-jan-2015#1596341">star pattern</a> here. There's just endless, clean, clear space for you to actually do the things you do. <a href="http://trilema.com/2016/how-to-participate-in-the-affairs-of-the-most-serene-republic/">Start today</a>, and help us build <a href="http://trilema.com/2016/i-am-firmly-against-universal-franchise/">a better tomorrow</a>.</p>
<p>Do not be that sad monkey that knows how to work the banana dispenser but only uses  that knowledge to feed the louder, more obnoxious, dumber other monkeys. The internet, through the twin pillars of Bitcoin and cryptography, finally allows you to entirely cut them out of the loop. You do not need to nor do you have to pay a dime in "tax" ; you do not need to nor do you have to use any of their poisonous offerings, from banks to "identity services" to anything else. You absolutely do not have to participate in the useless, dysfunctional construction of useless, stupid "people". Opt out. Opt out today. </p>
<p>Let them have the "positions of power", which they imagine to be powerful somehow in and of themselves, rather than because that's where you happen to be seated -- much in the vein an illiterate child might imagine his father can read because he's wearing glasses, not because his father can actually read. Let them have the whole rustbucket, and let them sink to the bottom of the sea atop it.</p>
<p>Your life is somewhere else. Welcome aboard.</p>

              <div>
                <div class="alignleft">&laquo; <a href="http://trilema.com/2017/america/">America!</a></div>
